This document explains how to build the sourceforge
HBA API wraper library from source.

##
# HBA API Wrapper Library
##########################

DEPENDENCIES

* autoconf
* autotools
* sysconftool
* automake
* libtool

PROCESS

1) Bootstrap, configure, make and make install
   # ./bootstrap.sh
   # rpm --eval "%configure" | sh
   # make
   # make install
